name: NOE Open Government Data - Bestandsliste
description: Catalog of open government datasets from the Lower Austria region.

data_themes.description: Full extraction of specific data themes not possible without catalog metadata. Must be mapped to EU Data Themes vocabulary upon inspection.

geotopics.description: Full extraction of specific ISO 19115 Topic Categories not possible without catalog metadata. Must be mapped to ISO 19115:2003 upon inspection.
